item.title: Why Altseason Failed — And Why 2026 Will Be About Proof, Not Predictions
item.description: Altseason never arrived — it turned into the altered version of the Banana Zone, where hype, predictions, and recycled narratives caused traders to slip and fall. In this episode, I break down why 2025’s altseason narrative failed and why 2026 won’t be about bold predictions, but proof: real infrastructure, real adoption, and real signals over noise. item.title: Keys to Soul Progress: Entering 2026 with Intention: A Spiritual Refocus with Dr. Judith
item.description: In this first episode of 2026, Dr. Judith explores the deeper, spiritual framework required to step into the new year genuinely.
